== 制作 ==
林克莱特表示，本片在背景的设置和故事情节方面都像是《{{link-en|年少輕狂 (1993年電影)|Dazed and Confused (film)|年少輕狂}}》精神上的“续集”<ref >{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/15/0225/08/AJ9LNJJ1000300B1.html |language= |title=《少年时代》输奖不失意 林克莱特或拍摄续集 |publisher=m1905电影网 |date=2015-02-25 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226005121/http://ent.163.com/15/0225/08/AJ9LNJJ1000300B1.html |archive-date=2015-02-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2014年10月13日于德州[[奥斯汀|奥斯汀]]开拍<ref>{{cite web|title=Loving 1980, where a solid mustache belongs on the dance floor not the sex offender registry|url=https://twitter.com/glenpowell/status/521855109630660608|publisher=twitter.com|accessdate=October 16, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304225754/https://twitter.com/glenpowell/status/521855109630660608|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=olv>{{cite news|title=Richard Linklater’s ‘That’s What I’m Talking About’ begins filming in Austin; Extras needed|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2014/10/15/richard-linklaters-thats-what-im-talking-about-begins-filming-in-austin-extras-needed/|accessdate=October 16, 2014|publisher=onlocationvacations.com|date=October 15, 2014|archive-date=2014-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110113319/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2014/10/15/richard-linklaters-thats-what-im-talking-about-begins-filming-in-austin-extras-needed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也在德州的Weimar、San Marcos、Bastrop、Elgin、[[聖安東尼奧_(德克薩斯州)|聖安東尼奧]]取景<ref name="olv" /><ref>{{cite news|last1=RANEY|first1=NICOLE|title=Wanna be in a Linklater film? Austin-area extras needed for possible Dazed and Confused sequel|url=http://austin.culturemap.com/news/entertainment/new-richard-linklater-movie-dazed-and-confused-sequel-casting-call-audition-extras/|accessdate=September 30, 2014|publisher=culturemap.com|date=September 30, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084937/http://austin.culturemap.com/news/entertainment/new-richard-linklater-movie-dazed-and-confused-sequel-casting-call-audition-extras/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和Taylor<ref>{{cite news|title=Dazed and Confused Sequel, ‘That’s What I’m Talking About’ Casting Call|url=http://www.projectcasting.com/casting-calls-and-auditions/dazed-and-confused-sequel-thats-what-im-talking-about-casting-call/|accessdate=November 1, 2014|publisher=projectcasting.com|date=October 28, 2014|archive-date=2014-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141105080403/http://www.projectcasting.com/casting-calls-and-auditions/dazed-and-confused-sequel-thats-what-im-talking-about-casting-call/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>拍摄。

== 发行 ==
2016年3月11日在[[西南偏南|西南偏南影展]]上首映，4月1日有限上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/everybody-wants-some-release-date-richard-linklater-1201708776/|title=Richard Linklater’s ‘Everybody Wants Some’ Gets April 1 Release|publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Dave|last=McNary|date=February 17, 2016|accessdate=March 17, 2016|archive-date=2017-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170204164451/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/everybody-wants-some-release-date-richard-linklater-1201708776/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，4月15日正式公映<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Richard Linklater Baseball Comedy to Release April 15|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/richard-linklater-baseball-movie-release-date-1201549251/|accessdate=July 28, 2015|work=variety.com|date=July 27, 2015|archive-date=2016-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160523213615/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/richard-linklater-baseball-movie-release-date-1201549251/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 評價 ==
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度87%，基於191條評論，平均分為7.6/10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/everybody_wants_some/ |title=Everybody Wants Some!! (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=May 21, 2016 |archive-date=2016-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105160937/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/everybody_wants_some/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到83分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/everybody-wants-some!! |title=Everybody Wants Some!! Reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=May 18, 2016 |archive-date=2016-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122061408/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/everybody-wants-some!! |dead-url=no }}</ref>，收穫普遍好評。还被《[[时代杂志|时代杂志]]》评为年度十佳影片之列。<ref >{{cite web |url=http://www.1905.com/news/20161208/1137413.shtml |language= |title=《时代》杂志评选年度榜单 十烂之首竟然是这部 |publisher=1905电影网 |date=2016-12-08 |accessdate= |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220105558/http://www.1905.com/news/20161208/1137413.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

